%%{init: {'theme':'base','flowchart': {'htmlLabels': true},'themeVariables': {'fontFamily': 'Inter, Microsoft YaHei, sans-serif','lineColor':'#64748B','primaryTextColor':'#0F172A','primaryBorderColor':'#CBD5E1','primaryColor':'#F8FAFC'}}}%%
flowchart TB
  Buyer([买家])
  Seller([卖家])
  CS([客服/运营])
  WxPay([微信支付])

  subgraph Platform[平台服务]
    Order[Order Service<br/>退款规则判定]
    Conv[Conversation Service<br/>持续会话]
    Case[Case Service<br/>退款/争议工单]
    Payment[Payment Service<br/>退款执行与回调幂等]
    Notif[Notification Service]
  end

  Buyer -->|申请退款| Order
  Order -->|创建 refund request| Order
  Order --> RefundDecision{是否自动退款}

  RefundDecision -->|是| AutoApprove[自动通过]
  RefundDecision -->|否| ManualCase[转人工审核]

  AutoApprove --> Payment
  ManualCase -->|创建/更新退款工单| Case
  Case -->|分配处理人| CS
  CS -->|审核结论：通过/驳回| Case

  Case -->|驳回| Reject[退款驳回]
  Reject --> Notif

  Case -->|通过| Approve[退款通过]
  Approve --> Payment

  Payment -->|发起原路退款| WxPay
  WxPay -->|退款回调| Payment
  Payment -->|更新订单 REFUNDING→REFUNDED| Order
  Order --> Notif

  Buyer -->|订单争议沟通| Conv
  Seller -->|订单争议沟通| Conv
  Conv -->|POST /orders/:orderId/dispute-conversations| Conv
  Conv -->|生成/复用 dispute 会话| Chat[持续会话]
  Chat -->|客服介入分配| CS
  CS -->|上传证据/补充说明| Case
  Case -->|裁定（全退/部分退/不退）| Payment
